   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Establishment and management of humanitarian hubs and common services in North Eastern Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM will contribute to ensuring an adequate humanitarian response to theneeds of internally displaced persons (IDPs) and host communities in North Eastern Nigeria. Through the establishment of Humanitarian Hubs (HH), IOM&#x2019;s proposed action will provide humanitarian partners working in Maiduguri with a stronger logistical base and greater access in the North East.</narrative>
  </description>
